e ca. 1:18,000. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. LC copy imperfect: Hole in left middle. AACR2: 650/1; 651/2"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:40:00.297Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/77691674/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd376/g3764/g3764s/ct006177.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd376/g3764/g3764s/ct006177.gif#h=138&w=150", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd376:g3764:g3764s:ct006177/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1084&w=1175", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd376:g3764:g3764s:ct006177/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=2168&w=2351"], "index": 18, "language": ["english"], "location": ["massachusetts", "united states", "springfield"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2015-10-19t10:55:40", "2025-06-07t18:31:59.700000", "77691674"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "partof": ["cities and towns", "catalog", "geography and map division"], "score": 27.891178, "shelf_id": "G3764.S7F7 1903 .R5", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["election districts", "united states", "springfield", "springfield (mass.)", "massachusetts", "maps"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T16:18:09.713Z", "title": "Map of the city of Springfield, Massachusetts", "type": ["cartographic"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/77691674/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mb:batch_mb_allspice_ver01:data:sn83020847:00517171062:1927010601:0001/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.pdf", "segment_count": 14, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83020847/1927-01-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mb:batch_mb_allspice_ver01:data:sn83020847:00517171062:1927010601:0001/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.pdf", "segment_count": 14, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83020847/1927-01-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83020847/1927-01-06/ed-1/?sp=13"], "batch": ["mb_allspice_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/massachusetts/", "2/united states/massachusetts/hampden/", "3/united states/massachusetts/hampden/springfield/"], "contributor": ["boston public library"], "date": "1927-01-06", "dates": ["1927-01-06"], "description": ["MONEY and BUSINESS The Business Year The moderate slackening of busi ness activity In December has as yet proved nothing except that the pace of midsummer and early fall was too rapid to be kept up Whether this re tardation Is to be succeeded by a re vival early In the year or whether It is the first stage of a continuing slight recession la not a subject about which the New Year business forecasters could be expected to speak with as surance A year ago the prophets foresaw a contraction of activity be fore the end of 1826 brought about by a decline in building operations and in motor car production and per haps by an excess of instalment selling These prophecies were not fulfilled and 1926 exceeded the most optimistic expectations The current prophecies are predominantly optlm istie Yet if the decline in building was not pronounced in 1926 It may become so in 1927 and the curtail ment of motor car output which was avoided by the pulsing prospe ity of 1926 can more scientifically be brought within the range of 1927 fore casts particularly when the unsatis factoriness of the agricultural eco nomic situation is taken"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-08-18T00:09:30.894Z", "group": ["ndnp/mb", "massachusetts-boston-public-library"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83020847/1927-01-06/ed-1/?sp=13", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mb:batch_mb_allspice_ver01:data:sn83020847:00517171062:1927010601:0013/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=268&w=208", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mb:batch_mb_allspice_ver01:data:sn83020847:00517171062:1927010601:0013/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=536&w=417", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mb:batch_mb_allspice_ver01:data:sn83020847:00517171062:1927010601:0013/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1072&w=834", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mb/batch_mb_allspice_ver01/data/sn83020847/00517171062/1927010601/0013.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 13, "language": ["english"], "location": ["massachusetts", "united states", "hampden", "springfield"], "location_city": ["springfield"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["hampden"], "location_state": ["massachusetts"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["0", "5", "2", "7", "sn83020847", "6